snippet.title: Cabbie! Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Cabbie! demo is now available to download and play on Steam!

Play solo or team up with up to three friends, either locally or with Remote Play Together. The demo gives you access to play as the game’s first four characters, Cabbie, Nova, Clutch and Journey. After a short tutorial you get to take on two levels and a boss from the first world.

Steam link:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2540530/Cabbie/
